subtests.name: e.style['animation-timing-function'] = "linear()" should set the property value
e.style['animation-timing-function'] = "linear(0)" should set the property value
e.style['animation-timing-function'] = "linear(0, 1)" should set the property value
e.style['animation-timing-function'] = "linear(0 0% 100%)" should set the property value
e.style['animation-timing-function'] = "linear(0% 100% 0)" should set the property value
e.style['animation-timing-function'] = "linear(0 0% 50%, 1 50% 100%)" should set the property value
e.style['animation-timing-function'] = "linear(0, 0.5 25% 75%, 1 100% 100%)" should set the property value
e.style['animation-timing-function'] = "linear(0, 1.3, 1, 0.92, 1, 0.99, 1, 1.004, 0.998, 1 100% 100%)" should set the property value
e.style['animation-timing-function'] = "linear(100%)" should not set the property value
e.style['animation-timing-function'] = "linear(0% 1 50%)" should not set the property value
